ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係佢哋錯誤期待傳真社偏袒佢哋啫，<br />\n難得有持平同深入報導嘅媒體，我會繼續支持。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁呢啲有證有據作新聞又點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/07/16/139911/smrtcrack/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2016%2F07%2F16%2F139911%2Fsmrtcrack%2F&d=kJv22Oqxn%2BhnZT0L8cPygLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=83309e79\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/07/16/139911/smrtcrack/</a></blockquote><br />\n直接貼文plz,<br />\n我唔想幫容癌賺click rate</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾抺黑，由頭到尾都講唔出人地係作<br />\n<br />\n最多係報導角度問題<br />\n<br />\n先雞蛋挑骨頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143229_acb1978506ea8b9980fda1e7b1d9c787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143229_acb1978506ea8b9980fda1e7b1d9c787.jpg&h=6f9086dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n件事係攻擊坡仔<br />\n都可以講到係收坡仔錢拍攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143230_6d3be320b9f1a581568eb40ced39231b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143230_6d3be320b9f1a581568eb40ced39231b.jpg&h=544a1eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問人地資料來源，人地要轉私人對話唔公開，就屌人順便踩人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143231_405ece71679a3ac128cda6a00fa49874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143231_405ece71679a3ac128cda6a00fa49874.jpg&h=29acd921&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143231_017ad7f3c97a0017c35c8b8e91eec602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143231_017ad7f3c97a0017c35c8b8e91eec602.jpg&h=bff1956d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後寫一大堆技術野打稻草人<br />\n大意係坡仔出事部分同香港火車無關，加埋狗鐵癰乜柒專家睇過就當唔關香港事<br />\n<br />\n但傳真社一路係針對既係製造商，即係南車，指佢同時有幫港鐵整車，根本冇衝突<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143232_017ad7f3c97a0017c35c8b8e91eec602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143232_017ad7f3c97a0017c35c8b8e91eec602.jpg&h=5cb822cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：同行如敵國<br />\n見傳真社出事為求踩多兩腳，不惜幫狗鐵洗白"},{"pid":"e96e2befb86ebe13b04c645165a45f28cc8d7595","tid":394573,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由當初訪問林榮基，到踢爆林子健，個反差太大<br />\n上次客觀效果係針對中共跨境執法，今次就係幫中共一地兩檢掃清輿論障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點幫呢？<br />\n<br />\n傳真社既責任就係如實報導新聞<br />\n<br />\n林子健柒，傳真社揾到佢柒既資料並登出黎<br />\n<br />\n係咁多<br />\n<br />\n有咩後果責任係林子健，唔係傳真社<br />\n<br />\n定係你覺得佢地應該唔中立偏幫某一邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問題係傳真社既金主絕大多數都係黃絲泛民呢，佢地俾錢係想佢踢爆權貴黑幕，所謂真相同新聞都有好多類型<br />\n<br />\n睇返傳真社做法，我只係覺得捐錢果d黃絲泛民好on9者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔查之前點知真相係乜？<br />\n你事前已經知係林子健老作，所以傳真社唔應該查？</blockquote>所以同中共鬥，黃絲永遠輸就係咁解<br />\n中共俾錢大公文匯，大公文匯唔會做不利中共立場既事<br />\n黃絲比錢傳真社，傳真社基於「中立」，係可以做不利黃絲立場既事<br />\n你講公開中立，人地唔講，打交邊個贏？</blockquote>見到你呢D回應真係覺得好恐怖<br />\n為左贏公平公正既核心價值都可以放埋一邊<br />\n比你呢D思想上到位一樣係變第二個共產黨</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1ab81569de626fc9bfac7548886b969f278597","tid":394573,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T06:43:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>由當初訪問林榮基，到踢爆林子健，個反差太大<br />\n上次客觀效果係針對中共跨境執法，今次就係幫中共一地兩檢掃清輿論障礙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\