.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係佢哋錯誤期待傳真社偏袒佢哋啫，<br />\n難得有持平同深入報導嘅媒體，我會繼續支持。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁呢啲有證有據作新聞又點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/07/16/139911/smrtcrack/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.vjmedia.com.hk%2Farticles%2F2016%2F07%2F16%2F139911%2Fsmrtcrack%2F&d=kJv22Oqxn%2BhnZT0L8cPygLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=83309e79\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.vjmedia.com.hk/articles/2016/07/16/139911/smrtcrack/</a></blockquote><br />\n直接貼文plz,<br />\n我唔想幫容癌賺click rate</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n垃圾抺黑，由頭到尾都講唔出人地係作<br />\n<br />\n最多係報導角度問題<br />\n<br />\n先雞蛋挑骨頭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143229_acb1978506ea8b9980fda1e7b1d9c787.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143229_acb1978506ea8b9980fda1e7b1d9c787.jpg&h=6f9086dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n件事係攻擊坡仔<br />\n都可以講到係收坡仔錢拍攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143230_6d3be320b9f1a581568eb40ced39231b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143230_6d3be320b9f1a581568eb40ced39231b.jpg&h=544a1eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問人地資料來源，人地要轉私人對話唔公開，就屌人順便踩人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143231_405ece71679a3ac128cda6a00fa49874.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143231_405ece71679a3ac128cda6a00fa49874.jpg&h=29acd921&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143231_017ad7f3c97a0017c35c8b8e91eec602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143231_017ad7f3c97a0017c35c8b8e91eec602.jpg&h=bff1956d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後寫一大堆技術野打稻草人<br />\n大意係坡仔出事部分同香港火車無關，加埋狗鐵癰乜柒專家睇過就當唔關香港事<br />\n<br />\n但傳真社一路係針對既係製造商，即係南車，指佢同時有幫港鐵整車，根本冇衝突<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/143232_017ad7f3c97a0017c35c8b8e91eec602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F143232_017ad7f3c97a0017c35c8b8e91eec602.jpg&h=5cb822cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論：同行如敵國<br />\n見傳真社出事為求踩多兩腳，不惜幫狗鐵洗白</blockquote><br />\n傳真社咁多數據都叫捕風捉影，<br />\n輔仁班作者啲主觀文叫乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n輔仁有好多作者，篇嘢個作者咪依家成個地鐵發言人咁既<br />\nMTR Service Update"},{"pid":"980c5518280af390126c9a75ae0ec39fbf052d51","tid":394573,"uid":61105,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:38:43.000Z","msg":"我就係欣賞佢夠中立，只要係事實點解唔報得？<br />\n利申：有捐"},{"pid":"d7a2c9570004f5691a558e7dfec9ae4bab7be20b","tid":394573,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我就係欣賞佢夠中立，只要係事實點解唔報得？<br />\n利申：有捐</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a525bf046656198a714faf0e4526b73b7009fd36","tid":394573,"uid":134834,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:05:55.000Z","msg":"成班都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地中立咁報導晒出來<br />\n係要屈鳩人有問題<br />\n黃絲真係唔代表咩<br />\n人地不斷踢爆權貴政府d 19野...<br />\n樓主一定無撚留意啦..<br />\n利申: 開頭捐過一次100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"491379e54240c46e5ebbfeb67c77c68425a545c5","tid":394573,"uid":100811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:14:54.000Z","msg":"其實記者做一個專題 有口人"},{"pid":"960311332b387a2af815dcf82e6a1a1a49d0213a","tid":394573,"uid":100811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:18:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實記者做一個專題 有口人</blockquote><br />\n未打曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實記者做專題 有d 要做幾個月甚至一年<br />\n加上傳真社唔係普通傳媒 <br />\n而係調查機構 專做專題報道 <br />\n明報蘋果都係由佢到拎source <br />\n做完林子健就潛 係因為未出到第二篇啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b2d74dc0d2ffa05ba58720917a194051c1ecb3","tid":394573,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地中立咁報導晒出來<br />\n係要屈鳩人有問題<br />\n黃絲真係唔代表咩<br />\n人地不斷踢爆權貴政府d 19野...<br />\n樓主一定無撚留意啦..<br />\n利申: 開頭捐過一次100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n既然中立，下次可以考慮踢爆黃之鋒同梁天琦點樣同美國佬枱底交易"},{"pid":"54de7f5cfd2f78d2b9956e0db7d4a0e8f64277ba","tid":394573,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:35:50.000Z","msg":"傳假社"},{"pid":"64c9eecd9121b7fc89a14dd19a971868c73bdc6f","tid":394573,"uid":49316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T11:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成班都痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地中立咁報導晒出來<br />\n係要屈鳩人有問題<br />\n黃絲真係唔代表咩<br />\n人地不斷踢爆權貴政府d 19野...<br />\n樓主一定無撚留意啦..<br />\n利申: 開頭捐過一次100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我覺得淫主黨肥佬係on99 但一口咬定係佢就過佐火位。事後有retract但感覺已經左搖右擺<br />\n<br />\n同意佢地。invesgative reporting 係唔錯"}]}